data.description: Enjoy the beauty and fun at Lost Lake without the waterfront taxes! Fishing, swimming and boating! This one story home offers Lake Views from the living room  and a nice country feel with room to expand and more! Areas for gardens and flower beds and outdoor entertaining as well..Hottub, deck, whole house auxillary generator and holding tank for well which holds 500 gallons of water at all times. 2400 sf shop to take care of your hobbies and needs. Heat pump/Air, Free Standing Propane Stove. Den could serve as bedroom if need be.  Please use Showing Time.
